            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "普通なら校舎裏。あるいはどこかのカフェで、\r\n一緒にチョコパフェを食べるなどだが……。",
            "enText": "Usually behind the school building. Or, we \ncan go to a cafe somewhere and have a \nchocolate parfait together. ……",
