            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "さすがはメジロ家。スケールが違った……。\r\nまさかカカオの樹ごとプレゼントされるとは。",
            "enText": "That's the Mejiro family. The scale was \ndifferent.…… I had no idea that the entire \ncacao tree was given as a gift.",
