        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "実が成るまでには時間がかかりますので、\r\n少々お待ちくださいませ～。",
            "enText": "It will take some time for the fruits to \ngrow, so please wait a little while.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "少々って、どのくらい？",
                    "enText": "How much is a little?",
