        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "そうですね～。うかがった話ですと……\r\nだいたい4年ほど～。",
            "enText": "Yes, that's right. I heard about…… \nabout 4 years or so.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "の、のんびりすぎないか？",
                    "enText": "I think it's a little too \neasygoing, don't you?",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "の、のんびりすぎない？",
                    "enText": "Not too laid-back?",
                    "nextBlock": 12
