        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "実際に口にするまでには、とんでもなく\r\n時間がかかるようだった……。",
            "enText": "It seemed to take an inordinate amount of \ntime to actually say it. ……",
            "nextBlock": 13,
