        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "申し訳ありません～。でも、じっくり時間を\r\nかけた分、食べる時の感動もひとしおだと\n思いますのよ～。",
            "enText": "I apologize for the inconvenience. \nBut the more time you put into it, \nthe more impressive it will be when \nyou eat it. I think.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": -6442517053652654262
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": -737243223392518932
