            "pathId": -6890415837375614176,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "そういうものこそ召しあがってほしいと\r\n思いますの～。きっと忘れられない味が\nいたしますわ。",
            "enText": "It is precisely this kind of food that I \nwould like you to enjoy. I am sure it will \nhave an unforgettable taste.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それはそうかもな……",
                    "enText": "That may be true: ……",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "それはそうかもね……",
                    "enText": "That may be true: ……",
                    "nextBlock": 16
