            "pathId": -4737748342651065541,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさま、約束しますわ。この樹に\r\n実が成りましたら、わたくし自らがチョコを\nお作りすると。",
            "enText": "I promise you, trainer. When this tree bears \nfruit, I will personally I will make the \nchocolate myself.",
