        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……この分だと、各工程に1年はかかって\r\nしまう。苦笑しながら、2人でカカオ畑の\n景色を楽しんだ。",
            "enText": "At this rate, each step would take a \nyear.…… We laughed and enjoyed the view \nof the cacao fields together. We enjoyed \nthe view of the cacao fields.",
