            "pathId": 479516935166108714,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "変わるのは少しこわくもありますけれど、\r\n楽しみでもありますのよ～。変化もまた\nわたくしたちの宝。そして……。",
            "enText": "Change can be a little scary, but it is also \nsomething to look forward to! Change is also \nOur treasure. And…… is a good place to start.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "animData": [
